injury.description: Aug 20: After missing the last three weeks due to an undisclosed injury, Brisker returned to practice in a limited capacity Tuesday, Kevin Fishbain of The Athletic reports.

Aug 28: Allen missed practice Wednesday due to foot discomfort, but Bears general manager Ryan Poles said that the wide receiver should be fine for Week 1 against the Titans, Courtney Cronin of ESPN.com reports.
Aug 20: Byard did not participate in practice Monday due to a soft-tissue injury, Brad Biggs of the Chicago Tribune reports.
